ControlLock.Name: Control Lock
ControlLock.Description: Select to receive a notification when Control Lock has been turned on or off.

CookCycleCancelled.Name: Cook Cycle Canceled
CookCycleCancelled.Description: Select to receive a notification if the cooking cycle has been canceled.

CookModeChanged.Name: Cook Mode Changed
CookModeChanged.Description: Select to receive a notification if the cooking mode has changed.

CookTargetTempChanged.Name: Cook Target Temp Changed
CookTargetTempChanged.Description: Select to receive a notification if the oven cycle temperature has changed.

CookTimeComplete.Name: Cook Time Complete
CookTimeComplete.Description: Select to receive a notification when the oven timer has ended.

CookTimeCompleteReminder.Name: Cook Time Complete Reminder
CookTimeCompleteReminder.Description: Select to receive notifications every minute after the oven timer has ended until the oven has been shut off or the cycle has been adjusted.

CookTimerChanged.Name: Cook Timer Changed
CookTimerChanged.Description: Select to receive a notification when the oven timer starts or when the cook time has changed.

UpperCavityCulinaryInstructions.Name: Culinary Center Interruptions
UpperCavityCulinaryInstructions.Description: Select to receive a notification when the oven cycle requires manual interaction (i.e. removing foil cover, rotating dish).

KitchenTimerEventNotification.Name: Kitchen Timer Changed
KitchenTimerEventNotification.Description: Select to receive a notification if the kitchen timer has ended or been changed.

MeatProbeTargetChanged.Name: Meat Probe Target Changed
MeatProbeTargetChanged.Description: Select to receive a notification when the temperature for the meat probe has been changed.

MeatProbeTempAchieved.Name: Meat Probe Temp Achieved
MeatProbeTempAchieved.Description: Select to receive a notification when the meat probe has reached its set temperature.

Preheat25.Name: Preheat Cycle Progress
Preheat25.Description: Select to receive a notification when the preheat cycle is within 25 degrees of the set temperature

PreheatComplete.Name: Preheat Complete
PreheatComplete.Description: Select to receive a notification when the oven finishes preheating.

RemoteStatus.Name: Remote Enable Status
RemoteStatus.Description: Select to receive a notification when Remote Start has been turned on or off.

SelfCleanComplete.Name: Self Clean Completed
SelfCleanComplete.Description: Select to receive a notification when the self clean cycle is finished.
